Package main.java.boundaries

Class AdminDisplayForm

java.lang.Object
main.java.boundaries.AdminDisplayForm
All Implemented Interfaces:
Form
public class AdminDisplayForm extends Object implements Form
A form for administrative staff as a boundary level object to display various information about staff members. Administrators can view staff lists based on branch, role, gender, age, or display all staff members. This form is implemented from the Form interface.
